  "detailed_description": "<h1>Follow Us</h1><p>Join the community on our !</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>The Ghost Dragon has truly been killed, and the spiritualized dragon vein once again rises into the sky, tearing a passage between reality and the spirit world. A massive influx of spiritual energy and sinister forces floods into the magic city, empowering countless monsters and demons, causing them to wreak havoc in the human world once again. <br>The Investigation Bureau has no choice but to dispatch their staff members who are most capable of withstanding the dragon's power, a group of rational serpent demons, to deal with this anomaly.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/4bd672bfdd1f3cb3c7cc47c42fca1f34.avif?t=1713023800\" width=616 height=92 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/c8c36981ea1d66ea1d39eaa158303397.poster.avif?t=1713023800\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/c8c36981ea1d66ea1d39eaa158303397.webm?t=1713023800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/c8c36981ea1d66ea1d39eaa158303397.mp4?t=1713023800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Let your hungry little snake devour the elements it meets like a greedy snake<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/b7c63d4e95ae03874876104d88750b14.poster.avif?t=1713023800\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/b7c63d4e95ae03874876104d88750b14.webm?t=1713023800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/b7c63d4e95ae03874876104d88750b14.mp4?t=1713023800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Consume three identical elements to unleash skills to clear enemies<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/16b14c32f31e9c730d5ac2e23fc39c5f.avif?t=1713023800\" width=616 height=92 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/089c1d7980f1632e241cbc9b3eba8aa8.poster.avif?t=1713023800\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/089c1d7980f1632e241cbc9b3eba8aa8.webm?t=1713023800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/089c1d7980f1632e241cbc9b3eba8aa8.mp4?t=1713023800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Gain experience, Level up, Acquire enhancements and Create your  unique build<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/195fcf328cd796d53c18539b7a0649cc.avif?t=1713023800\" width=616 height=92 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/99bc50bc31e0f3fb5f0c01bcf77d5f96.poster.avif?t=1713023800\" width=616 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/99bc50bc31e0f3fb5f0c01bcf77d5f96.webm?t=1713023800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2574030/extras/9